    abbrev: "Ambro.",
    category: "plant",
    intro: "Rag-Weed (AMBROSIA) A remedy for hay-fever, lachrymation and intolerable itching of the eye-lids. Some forms of whooping-cough. Respiratory tract in its entire length stopped up. Many forms of diarrhoea, especially during summer months, also dysentery.",
