    intro: "Bromide of Arsenic Has proven a great anti-psoric and anti-syphilitic remedy. Herpetic eruptions, syphilitic excrescences, glandular tumors and indurations, carcinoma, locomotor ataxia, and obstinate intermittents, and diabetes are all greatly influenced by this preparation.",
    sections: {"Face": "Acne rosacea, with violet papules on nose; worse in the spring. Acne in young people."},
