    intro: "Buchu (BAROSMA CRENATA) Marked specific effects on genito-urinary system; muco-purulent discharges. Irritable bladder, with vesical catarrh; prostatic disorders. Gravel. Leucorrhoea.",
    sections: {},
    keynotes: ["Buchu (BAROSMA CRENATA) Marked specific effects on genito-urinary system", "muco-purulent discharges", "Irritable bladder, with vesical catarrh", "prostatic disorders"],
