    sections: {"Eyes": "Conjunctiva inflamed, swollen. Tearing pain in eyeballs; tension, forced-out feeling. Objects appear gray, upside down. Eye symptoms alternate with diminished hearing. Epiphora.", "Head": "Sensation as if brain were falling forwards; as from a blow on head.", "Respiratory": "Cough with sweat, pain and tightness of chest; larynx irritated."},
