    name: "Lamium Album",
    abbrev: "Lam.",
    category: "plant",
    intro: "White Nettle (LAMIUM) Has a special affinity for female and urinary organs. Headache, with backward and forward motion of head. Leucorrhoea and menses too early and scanty. Haemorrhoids; hard stool, with blood. Sensation in urethra as though a drop of water were flowing through it. Tearing in the extremities. Haemoptysis. Blisters on heel from slight rubbing. Ulcers on heel (Cepa).",
    sections: {},
