    sections: {"Head": "Anxious and depressed, confused. Vertigo; must close eyes. Head heavy. Noises in ears.", "Stomach": "Nausea, vomiting. Pain in pit of stomach and abdomen. Severe purging.", "Extremities": "Gait unsteady. Trembling of all limbs. Loss of power in extremities. Violent pain in calves, as if bound with cords. Cold extremities. Spasmodic motions of arms and legs. Cannot write; cannot hold a glass of water. Trembling of hands in paralysis."},
