    category: "plant",
    intro: "Moonseed (MENISPERMUM) A remedy for megrim, associated with restlessness and dreams. Pain in spine. Dryness, itching all over. Dry mouth and throat.",
    sections: {"Head": "Pressure from within outward, with stretching and yawning and pain down back. Sick headache; pain in forehead and temples, moving to occiput. Tongue swollen and much saliva.", "Extremities": "Pain in back, thighs, elbows, shoulders. Legs sore, as if bruised."},
