    category: "plant",
    intro: "Forget-me-not (MYOSOTIS) Chronic bronchitis and phthisis. Night-sweats.",
    sections: {"Respiratory": "Cough with profuse muco-purulent expectoration, gagging and vomiting during cough; worse while or after eating. Bronchorrhoea. Pain in left lung (lower); painful while coughing and sensitive to percussion."},
    keynotes: ["Forget-me-not (MYOSOTIS) Chronic bronchitis and phthisis", "Night-sweats"],
