    category: "plant",
    intro: "Brazilian Ucuba A remedy of great antiseptic powers. Inflammation of skin, cellular tissue and periosteum. Traumatic infections. Parotitis. Fistulas. Carbuncles. Specific action in panaritium. Pain in the finger nails with swelling of the phalanges. Hands are stiff, as if from squeezing something a long time. Coppery taste and burning in throat. Tongue white and cracked. Phlegmonous inflammations.",
    sections: {},
    keynotes: ["Brazilian Ucuba A remedy of great antiseptic powers", "Inflammation of skin, cellular tissue and periosteum", "Traumatic infections", "Specific action in panaritium"],
