    intro: "Paghala-malli-Sad Tree Bilious and obstinate remittent fever; sciatica; rheumatism. Constipation of children.",
    sections: {"Head": "Anxious and restless; dull headache. Tongue coated.", "Stomach": "Burning sensation, better cold application. Thirst, better vomiting.", "Abdomen": "Tenderness of liver. Profuse, bilious stool, with nausea. Constipation.", "Fever": "Thirst, before and during chill and heat; better vomiting as close of chill; sweat no marked."},
    keynotes: ["Paghala-malli-Sad Tree Bilious and obstinate remittent fever", "Constipation of children"],
