    sections: {},
    keynotes: ["Sorrel-tree (OXYDENDRON - ANDROMEDA ARBOREA) A remedy for dropsy-ascites and anasarca", "Urine suppressed", "Deranged portal circulation", "Prostatic enlargement"],
