    intro: "Hydropiper - Smartweed (POLYGONUM PUNCTATUM) Metrorrhagia, also Amenorrhoea in young girls. Varicosis; haemorrhoids and rectal pockets. Burning in stomach followed by feeling of coldness in the pit of the stomach.",
    sections: {"Abdomen": "Griping pain, with great rumbling, nausea, and liquid feces. Flatulent colic.", "Rectum": "Interior of anus studded with itching eminence. Haemorrhoids. Liquid feces.", "Urinary": "Painful constriction at neck of bladder.", "Female": "Aching pains in hips and loins. Sensation as if hips were being drawn together. Sensation of weight and tension within pelvis. Shooting pains through breasts. Amenorrhoea.", "Skin": "Superficial ulcers and sores on lower extremities, especially in females at climacteric."},
