    category: "plant",
    intro: "Cowslip Cerebral congestion, with neuralgia; migraine; rheumatic and gouty pains.",
    sections: {"Head": "Sensation of a band around head; cannot keen hat on (Carbol ac). Skin of forehead tense. Fear of falling when standing up. Violent vertigo, as if everything turned around. Buzzing in ears; better in open air.", "Respiratory": "Cough, with burning and pricking in respiratory tracts. Weak voice.", "Urinary": "Urine smells strongly of violets (Terebinth).", "Extremities": "Right axillary muscles painful. Weight and lassitude in limbs, especially the shoulders. Burning in hollow of right hand. Drawing pain in thumb and big toe."},
