    intro: "Fragrant Sumach Renal and urinary affections, especially diabetes. Enuresis due to vesical atony; senile incontinence. Haematuria and cystitis come within the range of this remedy.",
    sections: {"Urine": "Pale, albuminous. Incontinence. Severe pain at beginning or before urination, causing great agony in children. Constant dribbling. Diabetes, large quantities of urine of low specific gravity (Phos ac; Acet ac)."},
    keynotes: ["Fragrant Sumach Renal and urinary affections, especially diabetes", "Enuresis due to vesical atony", "senile incontinence", "Haematuria and cystitis come within the range of this remedy"],
