    name: "Titanium Metallicum",
    abbrev: "Titan.",
    category: "plant",
    intro: "The Metal (TITANIUM) Is found in the bones and muscles. Has been used in lupus and tuberculosis processes externally, also in skin disease, nasal catarrh, etc. Apples contain 0. 11 per cent of Titan. Imperfect vision, the peculiarity being that half an object only could be seen at once. Giddiness with vertical hemiopia. Also, sexual weakness, with too early ejaculation of semen in coitus. Bright\\'",
    sections: {},
